title: RHOBH An Inconvenient Tooth
itunes:title: RHOBH An Inconvenient Tooth
description:
Danny recaps The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured a dinner for Homeless Not Toothless, Dorit's charity, plus a Melissa Etheridge performance, a stretch expert for Splits, and Asher on the piano in an animal print blouse. Danny also shares an important Candace Cameron Boring detour! Hope everyone is having a nice week!
